<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Salomon '97 EPS view upped.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Salomon '97 EPS view upped.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Brown Brothers Harriman analyst Raphael Soifer said he raised his earnings estimate to $6.10 per diluted share from $5.50 for 1997.</p>
<p>-- kept the stock rated near-term hold, and long-term market perform.</p>
<p>-- cited Salomon's announcement that it was selling its Basis Petroleum unit to Valero Energy Corp.</p>
<p>-- shares fell 3/4 to 53-5/8.</p>
</text>
